                            <strong class="text-blue-300 block mb-1">The "Neighbor" Strategy</strong>
                            If your shop is in <strong>Bangsar</strong>, we create 10 pages targeting the immediate wealth: <strong>Damansara Heights, Mont Kiara, Sri Hartamas</strong>.
                            <div class="absolute top-full left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -mt-1 border-4 border-transparent border-t-slate-800"></div>
                        </div>
                    </li>

                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-slate-700">
                        <i data-lucide="zap" class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span>Lightning Fast & Secure Hosting</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-xs text-slate-700">
                        <i data-lucide="message-circle" class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span>Direct-to-WhatsApp Setup</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <a href="https://tally.so/r/aQ52Lv" target="_blank" class="w-full block text-center bg-white border-2 border-slate-200 text-slate-600 font-bold py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors text-sm">
                    Build Launchpad
