                        <i data-lucide="info" class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-500 mt-0.5"></i>

                        <div class="absolute bottom-full left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 mb-2 w-64 p-3 bg-white text-slate-900 text-xs rounded-lg shadow-xl opacity-0 invisible group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:visible transition-all duration-200 pointer-events-none">
                            <strong class="text-blue-600 block mb-1">The "City-Wide" Strategy</strong>
                            Total coverage. We generate pages for <strong>every</strong> viable neighborhood (Subang, PJ, KL, Cheras, Ampang). You capture traffic from the whole territory.
